{
  "stem": "1799.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And right from the beginning of my arrival there, again because I spoke German, a guard picked me out and said, you are going to be in charge.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Every day, you're going to be bearing corpses that are going to be located, you know, in this and this place.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we will have-- and they call that a [NON-ENGLISH] kommando.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we will have a guard walk with you every day and show you where you are to dig.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we did this the first day and dug a grave.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "By the way, this was near a highway to Augsburg.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If you draw a line from Munich to Augsburg, this place where we went to more or less every day, within, you know, a few hundred feet, I'm not sure-- I could probably pick it out, if unless they've already found it.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because the graves were probably not very deep.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were fairly shallow.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But we dug graves.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There were six, seven of us with picks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the stones in Bavaria are-- or rather, the soil in Bavaria is composed of stones, rather than just sandy soil.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So digging a grave there was trickier, having to remove large stones, and by hand even, you know, some of them the size of a head.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And-- but we managed to dig about an eight by eight feet by six or so feet deep daily.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And it so happened that daily, in turn, there were enough corpses to fit into this large hole, which we then covered.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then the next day, we would come with a new batch.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "This was [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] particularly, how shall I say, what was unusual about the procedure.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Procedure is a bad word.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
